This is a complex command that starts slow, and eventually snowballs up to be a high earning command if you keep up with it! Viewers: This is the number of viewers watching your stream. It will go up if you keep your stream up, and your viewer count directly affects your ad revenue. Sponsors: This is the number of stream sponsors you have. Sponsors can gift you coins or streaming items but asking for donations too frequently can end your stream. You can increase this by keeping your streak up! Streak: This is your daily streak of streaming. You want to get this as high as possible, and it's not affected by vacation at all. Ads: The run ads button is how you earn money, but it has a chance to end your stream. Chat: Reading chat is the safest option to keep your stream live, but it doesn't give you any coins or items. Dank Memer BOT 28-Dec-21 06:58 PM
Streaming Simulator
This is a complex command that starts slow, and eventually snowballs up to be a high earning command if you keep up with it! Here are some basic things to know: Interaction: You can interact every 10 minutes. You MUST interact at least once every 30 minutes to keep your stream live. Level: This is your streamer level. 100xp gains you another level. You can earn XP for keeping your stream alive longer. You earn XP at the end of a stream. Viewers: This is the number of viewers watching your stream. It will go up if you keep your stream up, and your viewer count directly affects your ad revenue. Sponsors: This is the number of stream sponsors you have. Sponsors can gift you coins or streaming items but asking for donations too frequently can end your stream. You can increase this by keeping your streak up! Streak: This is your daily streak of streaming. You want to get this as high as possible, and it's not affected by vacation at all. Ads: The run ads button is how you earn money, but it has a chance to end your stream. Chat: Reading chat is the safest option to keep your stream live, but it doesn't give you any coins or items. Streaming items: These special items are ONLY found from sponsors, and each item can change your stream. Read the description of items to see what they do with pls shop <item>. You use them with pls use <item>
(edited)
Missing Items!
To start your streaming journey, you need following items: - Keyboard - Mouse
